QuestData.Title: The Runewood's Revenge
QuestData.Description:
The Bonespeakers...they are corrupt... hungry for power.
Cut them from my woods...
QuestData.LogDescription: Kill 8 Bonespeaker Runeaxes and 8 Bonespeaker Carvers in the Runewood.
QuestData.RewardText: The Runewood will know peace once more with these Bonespeakers removed from the land. $B$BIt is a good beginning.
